Package: daytona-runner-ch
Version: ${VERSION}
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17), qemu-utils, iproute2, iptables, openssh-client
Maintainer: Daytona Platforms Inc <support@daytona.io>
Description: Daytona Runner for Cloud Hypervisor
 The Daytona Runner for Cloud Hypervisor provides virtual machine management
 capabilities for the Daytona platform using Cloud Hypervisor as the VMM.
 .
 Features:
 - Fast VM creation and boot
 - Live snapshot/restore for instant fork
 - GPU passthrough via VFIO
 - Hot-plug CPU and memory resizing
 - Network isolation via iptables
